snippet.title: KILL THE CUTE - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Now available on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2294950/Kill_The_Cute/

- Kill The Cute is a 2D Rogue-Lite game about killing cute things for no reason. You're the villain! Choose the best character that suits you, capture their souls, discover the most powerful skill builds, upgrade your characters and unchain your cute agression!

X: https://twitter.com/wcraft_official
Discord: https://discord.gg/shPww23hyg
